NextGen Academy is a dynamic e-learning platform built to deliver practical, affordable, and high-quality education in economics and business. Based in Malang, East Java, the platform empowers high school students, university students, and MSME (UMKM) owners with the real-world skills they need to grow.

---

## Key Features

- **Diverse Learning Formats** — E-learning videos, interactive content, intensive bootcamps, and one-on-one mentoring with industry experts, all in one place.
- **Accessible Pricing** — Courses starting from IDR 5,000, making quality education available to learners at every income level.
- **Lead Generation & Conversion** — A streamlined registration system with direct WhatsApp integration to facilitate student inquiries and smooth enrollment.
- **User-Centric Design** — A responsive interface with a clear FAQ section, designed for learners of all technical backgrounds.

---

## Tech Stack

Built with **Next.js** and modern web technologies, delivering a fast, SEO-optimized, and scalable educational platform.

---

## Our Contribution

> *"We didn't just build a website — we built an accessible gateway to quality education. The challenge was making a complex course catalog feel simple and inviting for learners who are not tech-savvy."*

Developed as part of the **Ariverse Studio** portfolio, this project demonstrates our ability to build robust, scalable educational platforms that bridge the gap between affordable pricing and high-quality digital learning experiences.
